WEBVTT

00:06.407 --> 00:08.509
Well, I thought Lisbeth
didn't wanna talk to you.

00:08.542 --> 00:10.244
And she's in rehab anyway,
right?

00:10.278 --> 00:11.479
Stay away from me.

00:11.512 --> 00:13.181
I just wanna know why you left.

00:13.214 --> 00:15.516
James is going to work
at the Facility.

00:15.549 --> 00:18.319
Please stop lying.

00:18.352 --> 00:20.788
You act like everything
is great, and it is not.

00:20.821 --> 00:22.523
My stomach.

00:25.393 --> 00:26.560
- Hello.
- My God.

00:26.594 --> 00:27.561
Sorry about the tie on the door.

00:27.595 --> 00:29.263
No, you're not.

00:29.297 --> 00:31.832
These last few days
have just been killing me.

00:31.865 --> 00:34.468
I will make up for it.
Every minute we've waited.

00:34.502 --> 00:37.105
I don't think that this
is the right fit anymore.

00:38.872 --> 00:40.484
I'm gonna give you the movie
that I've been dreaming about.

00:40.508 --> 00:42.243
Megan is your star.

00:42.276 --> 00:43.820
I'm not gonna actually act
in the movie at all.

